  "title": "Pricing / Costing Finance Analyst ( Public Healthcare Sector - Jurong East ) [ Degree in Accountancy ] Up 5.5K #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Liaise and work closely with various stakeholders in performing cost calculation and pricing on existing and new services/ projects.</li>\n  <li>Ensure Service master is updated and accurate for system go-live.</li>\n  <li>Prepare, formulate, and rationalise price revision proposal to ensure organisation’s financial sustainability, while taking into consideration patient bill impact.</li>\n  <li>Work with IT vendor to maintain efficient SharePoint workflow as part of continuous process improvement, including the identification and resolution of issues.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and report SharePoint workflow turnaround time.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accurate and timely update of data files for internal management reporting.</li>\n  <li>Support annual cost refresh/ updates on services.</li>\n  <li>Provide Business partnering support to Business Units within a growing regional healthcare system.</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Business/ Admin/ Account/ Finance</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in Pricing and Costing will be advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p>\n<p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
